{"tid":2436882,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點解香港人改英文名咁鳩","createTime":"2021-03-07T13:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T15:57:57.000Z","uid":209198,"like":7,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8bfa30d892a793d96cd48f34e1741c62fda30166","tid":2436882,"uid":209198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:00:31.000Z","msg":"有啲老套啲既<br />\n男：Ben Ken <br />\n女：May Jenny<br />\n呢啲都算<br />\n起碼叫正常名先<br />\n<br />\n但有啲名（特別係女人名）<br />\n真係係外國得Stripper先會用<br />\n例如Candy Rainbow Apple Cherry<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後有一堆名又改到奇奇怪怪<br />\n根本唔suppose係用黎做英文名既字又攞黎用<br />\n動物名：Tiger Rabbit <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n職業名：聽過有人叫Fireman但係女黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n數字：Zero One真係以為自己係動漫主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n天氣：呢個真係大撚把 Rain Sunny Thunder 一口氣寫出黎以為自己睇緊天氣預報<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自然：Spring Summer Autumn Cloud Snow Rock Ocean...例子太多講都講唔曬 真係一言難盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食物飲品：Coffee Mocha Banana Orange<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋其實有個問題係我咁多年以黎都無諗過<br />\n但係外國friend講完之後就覺得好奇怪<br />\n例如陳大文 英文名咪Chan Tai Man<br />\n無啦啦又要加多個名 當你叫Sam咁先算啦<br />\n呢個做法亞洲區真係應該得芝麻人/香港人/台灣人先會咁做<br />\n香港人之間溝通叫全名咪算囉<br />\n同外國人溝通咪叫自己First name/Surname囉<br />\n你試下填啲正式form寫自己叫Sam Chan睇下得唔得<br />\n（你證件上面嗰名既格式係咁就由佢啦）<br />\n根本無啦啦搞多個英文名呢個文化本身就多鳩餘<br />\n就算係因為方便溝通先咁做<br />\n但改到咁柒 我係鬼佬都唔知笑你定叫你好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a466868b7b6d642b8801c8db4c9cb2ca6713e4","tid":2436882,"uid":388119,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:02:22.000Z","msg":"有乜所謂<br />\n有個鬼佬中文名夠叫激烈的海膽"},{"pid":"ebdd308aaca6eb48a4accdcd9374a190fbbe846f","tid":2436882,"uid":209198,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"38a466868b7b6d642b8801c8db4c9cb2ca6713e4","tid":2436882,"uid":388119,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:02:22.000Z","msg":"有乜所謂<br />\n有個鬼佬中文名夠叫激烈的海膽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:05:11.000Z","msg":"所以咪就係比中文user笑鳩佢囉<br />\n依家唔係話改英文名好有問題天地不容<br />\n咁有時候真係會容易溝通左既<br />\n而係唔好改得咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9302cf09a1d8e85dd551944d3bace759588c9434","tid":2436882,"uid":1259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:07:01.000Z","msg":"咁不如你比一個正常嘅人名清單"},{"pid":"a87ad69dc120b80348a988e60f6c4d5f5a6ff983","tid":2436882,"uid":58089,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9302cf09a1d8e85dd551944d3bace759588c9434","tid":2436882,"uid":1259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:07:01.000Z","msg":"咁不如你比一個正常嘅人名清單"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:08:45.000Z","msg":"樓主物以類聚識埋D人英文名都怪過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以為自己看透世事咁"},{"pid":"27b174f134ad89724da44567f44998728396efcf","tid":2436882,"uid":197563,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9302cf09a1d8e85dd551944d3bace759588c9434","tid":2436882,"uid":1259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:07:01.000Z","msg":"咁不如你比一個正常嘅人名清單"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:23:31.000Z","msg":"Hugo"},{"pid":"65a5799a3cded04d150a1a0ecca79524b7fa406a","tid":2436882,"uid":342115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:27:26.000Z","msg":"英文名係易叫啲啫 <br />\n唔通吓吓都Tai Man, Ho Yin咩<br />\n轉個頭啲鬼佬肯定唔記得邊個打邊個"},{"pid":"796b13c77d0d89cbc332fcd1ea758baaced61bb4","tid":2436882,"uid":324456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:35:55.000Z","msg":"Fire, ice<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"accc7a082f10011a4718498258d288b7dbdca797","tid":2436882,"uid":252972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65a5799a3cded04d150a1a0ecca